headline: Prediction: Buying United Airlines Stock Today Will Set You Up for Life
summary: It's no secret that the airline industry is now facing headwinds from the uncertainty created by President Donald Trump's tariff plans.  Indeed, United Airlines (NASDAQ: UAL) and Delta Air Lines (NYSE: DAL) recently walked back full-year projections.  In that context, here's a look at why United is an excellent value stock for long-term investors.
